SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT QUOT_DATUM , QUOT_TIJD , QUOT_BIED , QUOT_LAAT , QUOT_FACTOR , QUOT_RECIPROKE FROM ( SELECT QUOT_SYMBOOL , QUOT_OPTIETYPE , QUOT_EXPIRATIEDATUM , QUOT_EXERCISEPRIJS , QUOT_SOORT , QUOT_DATUM , QUOT_BIED , QUOT_LAAT , QUOT_TIJD , QUOT_FACTOR , QUOT_RECIPROKE , ROW_NUMBER() over ( ORDER BY QUOT_SYMBOOL ASC , QUOT_OPTIETYPE ASC , QUOT_EXPIRATIEDATUM ASC , QUOT_EXERCISEPRIJS ASC , QUOT_SOORT ASC , QUOT_DATUM DESC , QUOT_TIJD DESC ) RN FROM fn_quotes_vw WHERE QUOT_SYMBOOL = ~1 AND QUOT_OPTIETYPE = ~2 AND QUOT_EXPIRATIEDATUM = ~3 AND QUOT_EXERCISEPRIJS = ~4 AND QUOT_SOORT BETWEEN ~5 AND ~6 AND QUOT_DATUM <= ~7 ) WHERE RN <= 1
